{"title":"【美文欣赏】万物静","slug":"wanwujing","date":"2022-10-12T13:03:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-18T05:59:57.258Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/wanwujing.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"        silence    <br><br>      <br>        <br/><br/><br/>  <br/><br/><br/>              万物静                文字｜温柔的药","covers":["https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202202/06/220642mrkhx6d8wxiaafkk.jpg"],"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"ie=edge\">\n  <title>silence</title>\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <br><br>\n  <section class=\"_editor\" style=\" margin: 0px auto;width:660PX;\">\n  <div class=\"item-content\"><section style=\"padding:20px 0px;\">\n  <br><section style=\"border: 1px dotted rgb(118,162,103);\">\n  <section style=\"margin: -10px 8px; border: 1px dotted #A5DAAA; box-shadow: #A5DAAA 0px 0px 1px ; background-color: #F5FFF6;\">\n  <section style=\"background-image: url('https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202202/06/214033r1ozun0d622ptwli.png'); background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;background-size:100%;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 50px 0px 10px;\">\n  <br/><br/><br/>\n  <br/><br/><br/>\n  <section class=\"_editor\">\n  <section style=\"margin: 10px auto 10px 6px;\">\n  <section style=\"text-align: left; letter-spacing: 5px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 16px; color: #17793C; text-shadow: #ffffff 1px 1px, #ffffff 1px -1px, #ffffff -1px 1px, #ffffff -1px -1px, #ffffff 0px 1.4px, #ffffff 0px -1.4px, #ffffff -1.4px 0px, #ffffff 1.4px 0px, #17793C 2px 2px, #17793C 3px 3px, #17793C 3px 1px, #17793C 1px 3px, #17793C 1px 1px, #17793C 2px 3.4px, #17793C 2px 0.6px, #17793C 0.6px 2px, #17793C 3.4px 2px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box;\" align=\"center\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 38px;\">\n  <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">万物静</span>\n  </strong>\n  </span>\n  </section></section></section></section>\n  <section data-id=\"100928\">\n  <section style=\"margin: 10px auto;text-align: center;\">\n  <section style=\"display: inline-block;\">\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 20px; padding: 4px 1.0em; color: #ffffff; border: 3px solid #ffffff; box-shadow: #ffffff 0px 0px 2px ;border-radius: 20px; background: #17793C;\">\n  文字｜温柔的药\n  <span id=\"more\"></span> \n  </section></section></section></section></section>\n  <p>\n  <br/>\n  </p>\n  <section class=\"_135editor\">\n  <section style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;\" data-id=\"91718\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 100%\" data-width=\"100%\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 360px;margin: 0 auto\">\n  <section data-role=\"square\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 360px; height: 180px;border: 8px solid #ffffff; box-shadow: #A5DAAA 0px 0px 1px ;border-radius: 0px 0px 180px 180px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; background-image: url('https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202202/06/220642mrkhx6d8wxiaafkk.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center;\">\n  <img data-width=\"100%\" src=\"https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202202/06/220642mrkhx6d8wxiaafkk.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width:100% !important;height: auto;opacity: 0;visibility: visible !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037037037037\" data-w=\"1080\"/>\n  </section>\n  </section></section></section></section>\n  <br><br>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 2.0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-right: 100px; margin-left: 100px;\">\n  <span style=\"color: #7DB884; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 15px;\">\n  <section class=\"box-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: -8px;\">\n  <section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n  <section style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;border-radius: 100%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 16px;width: 30px;height: 30px;background: #17793C;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;color: #f2f2f2;border-radius: 100%;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n  01\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;color: #333;flex: 1;text-align: left;color: #fff;margin-left: -10px;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: #17793C;\">　</span>\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"border-left: 1px solid #17793C; padding-left: 10px; margin-left: 1.3em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section><section>\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\" class=\"135brush\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%); color: #17793C; padding: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;border-radius: 15px;\">\n  我有动听的小名，昏昏然书写昨日送到的露珠<br>\n  你给的美好不限于此<br>\n  夜雨飘过，想念与晴朗即刻到来<br>\n  </section></section></section></section></section></section>\n  <section class=\"box-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: -8px;\">\n  <section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n  <section style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;border-radius: 100%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 16px;width: 30px;height: 30px;background: #17793C;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;color: #f2f2f2;border-radius: 100%;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n  02\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;color: #333;flex: 1;text-align: left;color: #fff;margin-left: -10px;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: #17793C;\">　</span>\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"border-left: 1px solid #17793C; padding-left: 10px; margin-left: 1.3em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section><section>\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\" class=\"135brush\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%); color: #17793C; padding: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 15px;line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;border-radius: 15px;\">\n  用你的指尖挑选动听，当我想到远方<br>\n  想到冬天的结尾处有人如你<br>\n  说点情话，再说点伤感<br>\n  </section></section></section></section></section></section>\n  <section class=\"box-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: -8px;\">\n  <section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n  <section style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;border-radius: 100%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 16px;width: 30px;height: 30px;background: #17793C;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;color: #f2f2f2;border-radius: 100%;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n  03\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;color: #333;flex: 1;text-align: left;color: #fff;margin-left: -10px;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: #17793C;\">　</span>\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"border-left: 1px solid #17793C; padding-left: 10px; margin-left: 1.3em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section><section>\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\" class=\"135brush\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%); color: #17793C; padding: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;border-radius: 15px;\">\n  今晚，月亮会看到你的眼睛<br>\n  我慢慢地经过，带头说起阴晴无定那么必然<br>\n  每段故事等待石头问路，与芳草依偎<br>\n  </section></section></section></section></section>\n  <section class=\"box-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: -8px;\">\n  <section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n  <section style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;border-radius: 100%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 16px;width: 30px;height: 30px;background: #17793C;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;color: #f2f2f2;border-radius: 100%;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n  04\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;color: #333;flex: 1;text-align: left;color: #fff;margin-left: -10px;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: #17793C;\">　</span>\n  </section></section>\n  </section><section style=\"border-left: 1px solid #17793C; padding-left: 10px; margin-left: 1.3em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section><section>\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\" class=\"135brush\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%); color: #17793C; padding: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;border-radius: 15px;\">\n  把闲置多时的水波晃动晃动<br>\n  你看起来大方明亮。我不会随意在唇上涂抹什么<br>\n  当你打开朝向我的窗户<br>\n  </section></section></section></section></section>\n  <section class=\"box-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: -8px;\">\n  <section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n  <section style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;border-radius: 100%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 16px;width: 30px;height: 30px;background: #17793C;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;color: #f2f2f2;border-radius: 100%;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n  05\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;color: #333;flex: 1;text-align: left;color: #fff;margin-left: -10px;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: #17793C;\">　</span>\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"border-left: 1px solid #17793C; padding-left: 10px; margin-left: 1.3em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section><section>\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\" class=\"135brush\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%); color: #17793C; padding: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;border-radius: 15px;\">\n  异乡与陌生，并不等同<br>\n  穿过一月寒风的我们没有拥抱。那就坐下来<br>\n  让一些字目睹相逢<br>\n  </section></section></section></section></section>\n  <section class=\"box-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: -8px;\">\n  <section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n  <section style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;border-radius: 100%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 16px;width: 30px;height: 30px;background: #17793C;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;color: #f2f2f2;border-radius: 100%;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n  06\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;color: #333;flex: 1;text-align: left;color: #fff;margin-left: -10px;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: #17793C;\">　</span>\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"border-left: 1px solid #17793C; padding-left: 10px; margin-left: 1.3em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section><section>\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\" class=\"135brush\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%); color: #17793C; padding: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;border-radius: 15px;\">\n  有人送来灯笼，说厮守与死守为了一只兔子<br>\n  这就是一个玩笑<br>\n  我准备另外种几棵大树，长满刺与轻狂<br>\n  </section></section></section></section></section>\n  <section class=\"box-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: -6px;\">\n  <section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n  <section style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;border-radius: 100%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n  <section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 16px;width: 30px;height: 30px;background: #17793C;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;color: #f2f2f2;border-radius: 100%;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n  07\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;color: #333;flex: 1;text-align: left;color: #fff;margin-left: -10px;\">\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">\n  <span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: #17793C;\">　</span>\n  </section></section></section>\n  <section style=\"border-left: 1px solid #17793C; padding-left: 10px; margin-left: 1.3em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section style=\"padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <section>\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\" class=\"135brush\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f2f2 10%, #F2FAF3 100%); color: #17793C; padding: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;border-radius: 15px;\">\n  年末的话要藏在箱底<br>\n  如果我是怀旧的，如果手还有翻动的欲望<br>\n  与你说遍来年好风光，人间的炊烟不断飘扬<br>\n  </section></section></section></section></section>\n  <br><br><br><br>\n  <div align=\"center\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n  document.write(\"<scr\"+\"ipt src='http://webftp.bbs.hnol.net/sxrx2016/players/jquery.js'></sc\"+\"ript>\")\n  document.write(\"<scr\"+\"ipt src='http://webftp.bbs.hnol.net/sxrx2016/players/player.js'></sc\"+\"ript>\")\n  document.write(\"<scr\"+\"ipt src='http://webftp.bbs.hnol.net/sxrx2016/players/songplay/player/songplay.js'></sc\"+\"ript>\")\n  </script>\n  </section>\n  </div>\n  <br><br>\n  </body>\n  </html>","categories":[{"name":"美文","slug":"美文","count":2,"path":"api/categories/美文.json"}],"tags":[]}